settings.description: Welcome to my first level, I hope you enjoy this level that I have made, some A coins are hidden and E coin is locked, good luck getting all of them. =D
Mario explores a dense world and was trapped by some ghosts from a very haunted mansion, in which he falls from the bottom and Mairo tries to climb to the top to find his most beloved home
This is just for fun. You can fly around with the power up.
I wanted to do a very complete level 0-0

A switch abundance! And surprisingly, you need to use them..

--Intended with any character--

Vanquish the Palace of the Koopas as you dodge vicious traps and tricks!

--Significantly harder as Luigi--

Solve puzzles, fill in empty spaces, set record time .. and play sudoku. Except it isn't sudoku? I'm baffled at what it's called. 

Hint: Make sure not to have a starman while getting a goomba's shoe.
You need to master number block swimming to beat this one. Watch out for Big Bass! Now with an E-Coin.

Ah, the wonders of the underground desert...

--Intended with any character, its basically the same experience)--

How are your platforming skills doing these days? Sorry if the music doesn't fit the level, but I just love it so much! You must fight gravity to get the e coin and one Ace coin!
Difficulty: 4/5
